      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Excel XLS</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">XLS is a proprietary binary file format used for Microsoft Excel spreadsheet which features calculation, graphing tools, pivot tables and a macro programming language.</skos:definition>
