      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">MPEG-4</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="et">MPEG-4</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">MPEG-4 – Moving Picture Experts Group – is a method of defining compression of audio and visual (AV) digital data. It was designated a standard for a group of audio and video coding formats and related technology.</skos:definition>
