      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="et">PDF/X</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">PDF/X is a subset of the PDF standard. The purpose of PDF/X is to facilitate graphics exchange, and it therefore has a series of printing related requirements which do not apply to standard PDF files.</skos:definition>
