      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="et">PDF/A-2a</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">PDF/A-2 is the Part 2 of the PDF standard and specifies three levels of conformance for PDF files. PDF/A-2a corresponds to conformance level a in PDF/A-1 (accessible).</skos:definition>
