      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">PowerPoint PPTX</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">PPTX – PowerPoint 2007 XML presentation – is an XML filename extension of Office Open XML version of Microsoft PowerPoint presentation program. PowerPoint was originally designed to provide visuals for group presentations within business organizations, but has come to be very widely used in many other communication situations, both in business and beyond.</skos:definition>
      <dc:identifier>PPTX</dc:identifier>
      <atold:op-code>PPTX</atold:op-code>
