      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="et">RDF XML</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">RDF XML</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">RDF XML is a syntax, defined by the W3C, to express (i.e. serialize) an RDF graph as an XML document.</skos:definition>
