      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">AKN4EU file</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="et">AKN4EU fail</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">AKN4EU file is an Akoma Ntoso XML file conforming to the AKN4EU (Akoma Ntoso for European Union) specifications. One or more AKN4EU files can be part of an AKN4EU ZIP file. A special AKN4EU file called ‘main.xml’ is the entry point of an AKN4EU ZIP file.</skos:definition>
