      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="et">Kompressitud LAS fail</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Compressed LAS file</skos:prefLabel>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">LAZ is the media type which shall be used for compressed LAS files. This media type is incomplete as it lacks a reference to the specification of the format.</skos:definition>
